{"synckey":1596288384,"updated":[{"bookId":"25849523","bookmarkId":"25849523_3_2308-2344","chapterUid":3,"markText":"早期的人类在受伤和分娩时出血的风险很大，因此他们需要迅速有效地凝结血液。","range":"2308-2344","createTime":1596288384,"type":1},{"bookId":"25849523","bookmarkId":"25849523_3_967-1019","chapterUid":3,"markText":"早期的人类为了避免饥饿，需要在任何有食物的时候填饱自己的肚子。如今，我们吃得远比我们的身体真正需要的多。","range":"967-1019","createTime":1596288327,"type":1},{"bookId":"25849523","bookmarkId":"25849523_3_1868-1925","chapterUid":3,"markText":"我们的祖先总是面临致命的脱水威胁，特别是当他们锻炼和出汗的时候，所以他们的身体有着对水和盐的渴求和保存它们的冲动。","range":"1868-1925","createTime":1596288316,"type":1},{"bookId":"25849523","bookmarkId":"25849523_3_2184-2231","chapterUid":3,"markText":"我们的高度警觉、恐惧以及担心导致了越来越常见的焦虑、抑郁和创伤后遗症，以及它们可能造成的自杀。","range":"2184-2231","createTime":1596288303,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"前言","chapterUid":3,"chapterIdx":3}],"book":{"bookId":"25849523","version":1066765106,"format":"epub","soldout":1,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://wfqqreader-1252317822.image.myqcloud.com/cover/523/25849523/s_25849523.jpg","title":"反本能生存学：我们是如何被四项关键生存特性摧毁的","author":"李·戈德曼","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KDOYSCo1|dWVo1$6|KSMJk","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#370e17"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#400115"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#480015"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#4d2526"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#571d21"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#61101c"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#693b37"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#74342f"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#7f2a27"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#940016"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#8f4d46"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#a63d34"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#82544f"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#c4584a"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#9b6e68"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#b76154"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#b58981"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#c48378"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#d27c6d"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#ec6c58"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#f09685"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#fd8f7b"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#ff866f"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#ecbdb4"},{"key":"8/6","hex":"#fdb7a9"},{"key":"8/12","hex":"#ff9e83"},{"key":"9/2","hex":"#f2dfdb"},{"key":"9/12","hex":"#ffb79f"